# ❌ Common Mistakes

🔴 Using Selling Price (SP) instead of Cost Price (CP) while calculating percentage.

🔴 Forgetting whether the question asks for Profit or Profit %.

🔴 Adding instead of subtracting.

🔴 Confusing Profit with Loss.

🔴 Calculation mistakes while dividing.

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# 🎯 Interview Tips

### Step 1

Identify whether

```text
SP > CP

or

CP > SP
```

### Step 2

Find Profit or Loss.

### Step 3

If percentage is asked,

Always divide by **Cost Price (CP)**.

Never divide by Selling Price.

